law.catch_line: Information on revenue bonds issued by Commonwealth to be assembled and published.
law.text: Information on revenue bonds issued by the Commonwealth and by the agencies and institutions thereof shall be assembled and published under the direction of the secretary of the Finance and Administration Cabinet.
law.history: Created 1956 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 7, Art. XVI, sec. 14, effective July 1, 1956.
